name: My Aunt's Cats
description:
Nobody's heard from Aunt Felicity for a while, it's about time somebody checks on her.

Made for List Jam 2, using these themes:

  • Cabin in the woods with a monster
  • Cats Everywhere

Use the mouse to move around and inspect parts of the house!

Credits:

Gunturtle - Artwork and sound

Retrisma - Code and additional sound
